---
description: Senior backend challenge rules for AI collaboration logging and semantic safety
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow `AGENTS.md` for every task in this repository.

- Append every meaningful AI step to `solutions/ai-collaboration-log.md`.
- Define overloaded terms before code changes: balance, cost, account, usage, stable, canary, provider, customer key.
- Do not update a canary service directly when it has public traffic.
- Record release decisions in `solutions/release-command-log.md`.
- Record semantic decisions in `solutions/decision-log.md`.
